{"tid":1561143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發！宣道會陳X芝記念中學疑似製造白色恐怖","createTime":"2019-09-11T13:15:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T13:42:31.000Z","uid":133038,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cfb7582f2a3361814da9c12058097a4d16b8a8af","tid":1561143,"uid":133038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:15:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0fM1cTA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0fM1cTA.jpg&h=e70fba57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家記得去支持下班學生<br />\n<br />\n12/9 屯門區聯校人鏈活動詳情<br />\n日期：12/9(星期四)<br />\n時間：由1700開始集合，到1730正式拖手直至大約1930<br />\n地點：由龍門居橋作起點，終點會在兆康附近。<br />\n沿路會有五大checkpoint:<br />\n1）Yuen yee bridge (即連接友愛到龍門居的橋)<br />\n2）友愛行人橋（1.2億橋）<br />\n3）屯西<br />\n4）蔡意橋輕鐵站<br />\n5）虹橋（譚李麗芬中學旁邊）<br />\n衣着：學生請穿着校服參與本次活動<br />\n活動目的：<br />\n1）五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n2）聲援被捕人士<br />\n3）追查警察濫權問題<br />\n4）要求公開831太子站CCTV片段<br />\n5）聲援中學生被學校打壓罷課問題<br />\n活動內容：<br />\n沿屯門河製作人鏈<br />\n在特定時間一同開手機燈唱《願榮光歸香港》<br />\n<br />\n活動需要家長或校友義工及街坊幫手支援<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4p8ro0G.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4p8ro0G.jpg&h=c4defce0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDTro0J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDTro0J.jpg&h=de0f29dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rygHGNq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrygHGNq.jpg&h=59539d33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bf0941ae7797aff6516e40fb3398a088addb14fe","tid":1561143,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:16:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ac51950e3a2fd856cdca9f7b9ac847dbab3fd03d","tid":1561143,"uid":12510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"認真，無咩野，純粹利申咋喎"},{"pid":"2b613acdc88d602dac50d14721fce6fd5bbbb257","tid":1561143,"uid":133038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e6c570052ff4704a5171aa9c6b2c77ec00177662","tid":1561143,"uid":64689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:20:45.000Z","msg":"叫你參加就守法<br />\n唔參加就唔好去<br />\n有咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97dfce72a070cd3411e28a82d956f1fc4a7c0b4a","tid":1561143,"uid":255897,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:20:49.000Z","msg":"做下啲門面嘢姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6696e8d58c0279c57973532189105db03c5f5381","tid":1561143,"uid":147892,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:23:56.000Z","msg":"你老母係到出埋啲咁既post就白色恐佈啦柒頭皮廢閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9fddda88c0d1ec5094f2628a1ce5ce2e09501b2","tid":1561143,"uid":78023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T13:33:03.000Z","msg":"提醒都唔撚比?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a0581